dmca.title: Resume-Templates wants copiers given the pink slip
dmca.body:
I am contacting you regarding a competitor duplicating the content of our website. The content has been duplicated word-for-word.

The copyrighted work at issue is the website www.resume-templates.com. The website www.winning-resume.com has duplicated the content from our website. It even left the former street address of our company on its license page http://www.winning
